<p>A bulleted list of three items should appear: alpha, beta, gamma.</p><p>----------</p><ul><li>alpha</li><li>beta</li><li>gamma</li></ul><p>----------</p><p>Nothing should appear between the rules. Hiero block (and all children) stripped entirely.</p><p>----------</p><hiero><table class="mw-hiero-table"><tr><td><img src="test.gif" alt="glyph"/></td></tr></table></hiero><p>----------</p><p>The text "Heading Level One" should appear as a bold heading.</p><p>----------</p><h1>Heading Level One</h1><p>----------</p><p>Nothing should appear between the rules. SVG block (and all children) stripped entirely.</p><p>----------</p><svg width="100" height="100"><defs/><g><path d="M 0 0"/><rect width="10" height="10"/></g></svg><p>----------</p><p>The text "Heading Level Two" should appear as a bold heading.</p><p>----------</p><h2>Heading Level Two</h2><p>----------</p><p>Nothing should appear between the rules. Math block (and all children) stripped entirely.</p><p>----------</p><math>x<sup>2</sup> + y<sup>2</sup></math><p>----------</p><p>The text "Heading Level Three" should appear as a bold heading.</p><p>----------</p><h3>Heading Level Three</h3><p>----------</p><p>The text "Heading Level Four" should appear as a bold heading.</p><p>----------</p><h4>Heading Level Four</h4><p>----------</p><p>Nothing should appear between the rules. Gallery tag (and all children) stripped entirely.</p><p>----------</p><gallery>Image:test.jpg|Caption text</gallery><p>----------</p><p>The word "four" should appear inline (text extracted from t: annotation tag name suffix).</p><p>----------</p><p>count: <t:four/></p><p>----------</p><p>Nothing should appear between the rules. Nowiki tag (and all children) stripped entirely.</p><p>----------</p><nowiki><b>this should not appear</b></nowiki><p>----------</p><p>Nothing should appear between the rules. Poem tag (and all children) stripped entirely.</p><p>----------</p><poem>This line should not appear.</poem><p>----------</p><p>The text "oikos" should appear inline (text extracted from tr: annotation tag name suffix).</p><p>----------</p><p>origin: <tr:oikos/></p><p>----------</p><p>Nothing should appear between the rules. Ref tag (lowercase, and all children) stripped entirely.</p><p>----------</p><ref name="test">This reference content should not appear.</ref><p>----------</p><p>The text "la" should appear inline (text extracted from lang: annotation tag name suffix).</p><p>----------</p><p>language: <lang:la/></p><p>----------</p><p>Nothing should appear between the rules. REF tag (uppercase, and all children) stripped entirely.</p><p>----------</p><REF NAME="test">This reference content should not appear.</REF><p>----------</p><p>The text "sharp" should appear inline (text extracted from gloss: annotation tag name suffix).</p><p>----------</p><p>meaning: <gloss:sharp/></p><p>----------</p><p>The word "bright" should appear bold.</p><p>----------</p><p><b>bright</b></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "noun" should appear inline (text extracted from pos: annotation tag name suffix).</p><p>----------</p><p>part of speech: <pos:noun/></p><p>----------</p><p>The word "gentle" should appear italic.</p><p>----------</p><p><i>gentle</i></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "Grek" should appear inline (text extracted from sc: annotation tag name suffix).</p><p>----------</p><p>script: <sc:Grek/></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "ameba" should appear inline (text extracted from alt: annotation tag name suffix).</p><p>----------</p><p>alternate: <alt:ameba/></p><p>----------</p><p>The expression "H2O" should appear with the 2 as a subscript.</p><p>----------</p><p>H<sub>2</sub>O</p><p>----------</p><p>The text "female" should appear inline (text extracted from id: annotation tag name suffix).</p><p>----------</p><p>identifier: <id:female/></p><p>----------</p><p>The expression "x2" should appear with the 2 as a superscript.</p><p>----------</p><p>x<sup>2</sup></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "c. (circa)" should appear (abbr with single-word title).</p><p>----------</p><p><abbr title="circa">c.</abbr></p><p>----------</p><p>The word "calm" should appear underlined.</p><p>----------</p><p><u>calm</u></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "AD (anno Domini)" should appear (abbr with multi-word title containing a space).</p><p>----------</p><p><abbr title="anno Domini">AD</abbr></p><p>----------</p><p>The word "old" should appear with strikethrough.</p><p>----------</p><p><s>old</s></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "f. (filius)" should appear with "f." rendered italic (italic element inside abbr).</p><p>----------</p><p><abbr title="filius"><i>f.</i></abbr></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "printf" should appear in code style.</p><p>----------</p><p><code>printf</code></p><p>----------</p><p>The word "tiny" should appear small.</p><p>----------</p><p><small>tiny</small></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "visible text" should appear (single unknown tag stripped, text content kept).</p><p>----------</p><p><unknowntag>visible text</unknowntag></p><p>----------</p><p>The word "large" should appear big.</p><p>----------</p><p><big>large</big></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "inner text" should appear (nested unknown tags stripped, innermost text kept).</p><p>----------</p><p><outertag><innertag>inner text</innertag></outertag></p><p>----------</p><p>The variable "count" should appear italic (var element renders as italic).</p><p>----------</p><p><var>count</var></p><p>----------</p><p>The text "visible span" should appear (span tag stripped, text content kept).</p><p>----------</p><p><span>visible span</span></p><p>----------</p><p>Three words should appear: "plain" normal, "strong" bold, "both" bold and italic.</p><p>----------</p><p>plain <b>strong</b> <b><i>both</i></b></p><p>----------</p><p>Four words should appear: "plain" normal, "bold" bold, "italic" italic, "triple" bold and italic and underlined.</p><p>----------</p><p>plain <b>bold</b> <i>italic</i> <b><i><u>triple</u></i></b></p><p>----------</p><p>Two separate paragraphs should appear with a blank line between them.</p><p>----------</p><p>First paragraph text here.</p><p>Second paragraph text here.</p><p>----------</p><p>Two blocks of text should appear separated by a line break (div elements).</p><p>----------</p><div>First div block.</div><div>Second div block.</div><p>----------</p><p>Three lines of text should appear on separate lines (br elements).</p><p>----------</p><p>Line one.<br/>Line two.<br/>Line three.</p><p>----------</p><p>The text "quoted passage" should appear indented (blockquote element).</p><p>----------</p><blockquote>quoted passage</blockquote><p>----------</p><p>A numbered list of three items should appear: first, second, third (ol+li elements).</p><p>----------</p><ol><li>first</li><li>second</li><li>third</li></ol><p>----------</p>